## 📖 Overview
The Diabetes Patient Readmission Analysis Dashboard is an end-to-end healthcare analytics project designed to identify the key factors influencing patient readmissions. Using hospital records of diabetic patients, this project applies data cleaning, SQL analysis, exploratory data analysis (EDA), and interactive dashboarding to uncover actionable insights that can help healthcare organizations improve patient outcomes and reduce readmission rates.

The project follows a complete analytics workflow from raw data processing to business intelligence reporting using Python, SQL, and Power BI.

---

## 🎯 Business Objective
Hospital readmissions are a major challenge for healthcare providers as they increase treatment costs, resource utilization, and patient risk.

This project aims to answer the question:

> **"What factors increase diabetes patient readmission?"**

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- **Python**
  - Pandas
  - NumPy
  - Matplotlib
- **SQL (MySQL)**
- **Power BI**
- **Excel**

