## 📂 Project Workflow

### 1. Data Cleaning & Preprocessing
- Handled missing values
- Removed duplicates
- Standardized categorical variables
- Categorized diagnosis codes
- Cleaned admission and discharge tables
- Created meaningful diagnosis categories

### 2. SQL Analysis
Performed structured analysis across multiple business areas:

#### 👥 Patient Analysis
- Total Patients
- Gender Distribution
- Age Distribution
- Average Medications by Age

#### 🏥 Hospital Analysis
- Admission Type Analysis
- Average Hospital Stay
- Lab Procedures Analysis
- Long Stay Patients

#### 🔁 Readmission Analysis
- Readmission by Age Group
- Readmission by Gender
- Readmission by Admission Type
- Readmission by Medical Specialty
- Readmission by Diagnosis Category

#### 💊 Medication Analysis
- Insulin Usage
- Diabetes Medication Analysis
- Medication Change Impact on Readmission

#### 🩺 Diagnosis Analysis
- Most Common Diagnoses
- Diagnosis vs Readmission
- Diagnosis vs Hospital Stay
- Diagnosis vs Medication Usage

### 3. Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
Performed:
- Univariate Analysis
- Bivariate Analysis
- Correlation Analysis
- Data Visualization

### 4. Dashboard Development
Designed an interactive healthcare dashboard inspired by the Apollo Hospitals theme.

---

